  "body": "<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bol6rIk.png\" alt=\"Hidden Isles\">\n<br> \n<br>\n<br>\nThe perfect mix of adventure, tech, magic, and more without sacrificing performance in the newest versions of Minecraft.\n<br>\n<br>\nHidden Isles is a collection of 250+ mods to capture the imagination of the player through Adventure (Bosses, More mobs), Exploration (Dimensions, Space, Biomes), Magic, and Tech (Create, Powah, AE2) in a variety of ways. Each mod was selected and configured with the intent of making your experience better as a player. \n<br>\n<br>\nHidden Isles is here for you to play configured Modded Minecraft in the latest versions of the game! You can fight Bosses, explore the darkest of caves, challenge your friends to duels, and explore the world of Hidden Isles like no other!\n<br>\n<br>\nJoin our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/JUee9ausGb\">Discord</a> for support!\n<br>\n<br>\n<font size=\"5\"><strong>Full Mod List:</strong></font>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/adorn\">Adorn</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/advancement-plaques-fabric\">Advancement Plaques</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bosses-of-mass-destruction\">Bosses of Mass Destruction</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bartering-station\">Bartering Station</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/boat-item-view\">Boat Item View</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bookshelf\">Bookshelf</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-resewn\">CIT Resewn</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chunky-pregenerator\">Chunky</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/clumps\">Clumps</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/controlling\">Controlling</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/corgilib\">CorgiLib</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cull-less-leaves\">Cull Less Leaves</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dark-paintings\">Dark Paintings</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/debugify\">Debugify</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/emi-trades-villager-trading-emi-plugin\">EMI Trades</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/easy-anvils\">Easy Anvils</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enchantment-descriptions\">Enchantment Descriptions</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/entity-collision-fps-fix-fabric\">Entity Collision FPS Fix</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/equipment-compare-fabric\">Equipment Compare</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/forge-config-api-port-fabric\">Forge Config API Port</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/horse-expert\">Horse Expert</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/iceberg-fabric\">Iceberg</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immediatelyfast\">ImmediatelyFast</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/inventory-profiles-next\">Inventory Profiles Next</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jade\">Jade 🔍</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/leaves-be-gone\">Leaves Be Gone</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/legendary-tooltips-fabric\">Legendary Tooltips</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/log-begone\">Log Begone</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/magnum-torch-forge\">Magnum Torch</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/morecullingextra\">More Culling Extra</a